Quoting @dundargoc:

> - dependency from file to target or file to file can be done with `DEPENDS` in `add_custom_command`;
> - dependency from target to file is done via `DEPENDS` in `add_custom_target`;
> - dependency from target to target is done via `add_dependencies`.

Ref: https://cmake.org/cmake/help/latest/command/add_custom_command.html
